1995 Race Results
Dallas County, Texas

The 1995 race was a 70-mile circuit of Dallas County repeated over 3 days. The team completing the race in the shortest period of time was declared the winner.

Overall Standings
Rank Team
1 Los Altos (Hacienda Heights, California)
2 Carthage (Carthage, Missouri)
3 Winston (Dallas, Texas)
